snippet.title: Bare Butt Boxing - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Bare Butt Boxing will launch on Steam and Nintendo Switch's Eshop on August 1st!

Steam Link : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1186660/Bare_Butt_Boxing/
Nintendo Switch : https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/bare-butt-boxing-switch/

Take control of mischievous aliens mesmerized by the sport of boxing as they battle it out all over our beloved planet Earth, unaware of the laws and traditions of human society.

Join us on Discord : https://discord.com/invite/GTa9eQptHC
Follow us on Twitter : https://twitter.com/Tuatara_Games
About us : https://tuataragames.com/
